room_title: Escape room "Oktoberfest" by Hill Country Escape in Fredericksburg (TX)
room_description: Your dance troupe has finally made it to Oktoberfest! With rooms hard to find in town, you were lucky to have the owner of a B&B call to offer you rooms when they heard you were the headliner.
